{"tid":1366180,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺D MK仔操到幾舊腹肌都當正自己好撚FIT好on9","createTime":"2019-07-26T01:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T05:14:14.000Z","uid":34419,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3748c98d9e084e3521438b776a0747747ac440d6","tid":1366180,"uid":34419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:26:30.000Z","msg":"想當年我讀完毅進去咗做警察<br />\n<br />\n前排MK撚狗咁撚我, 我就約佢隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放工去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔 <br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街，牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌無關"},{"pid":"b6d85c7c69212254b64ba1b9cec46c558ab8dad8","tid":1366180,"uid":25771,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eee40f564ca28901051eee0418d5a55d59d1513","tid":1366180,"uid":156509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:28:40.000Z","msg":"又放工又同學又校服，唔撚連戲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea15cc7aa63ee4ae2564988b47771acfa9fef9f","tid":1366180,"uid":170967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:02:59.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170a72726e40b5ec7640a3a45563a4ec7ec61811","tid":1366180,"uid":25758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:03:52.000Z","msg":"潮文呢股風氣幾時完<br />\n有咩討論價值？"},{"pid":"7056b20ba7638706d6707f442260ad035211c2d5","tid":1366180,"uid":10141,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"170a72726e40b5ec7640a3a45563a4ec7ec6